content: Keep the hoards of interested men away from you when you’re out and about by wearing this “Married AF” shirt. This unisex shirt sports a comfy, snug fit and comes in a fashionable heather grey that’ll go well with a number of styles.

titleEN: People I Want To Punch Journal
content: Why take the high road when revenge feels so much sweeter? Using this “people I want to punch in the face” journal you’ll have ample room to write down everyone who has ever made the mistake of crossing you – so you can plan your vengeance.

Bring a small piece of the enchanting nighttime sky into your bedroom using this crescent moon light. It’s handmade using a metallic frame, satin, and fairy lights  which give off a soft glow – making this an ideal nightlight for the kids.

Give snacktime a healthy(ish) twist by trying one of these natural ingredients lollipops. Each lollipop is handmade from all-natural ingredients and complemented with organic fruit slices paired with other fruits and nuts.

Celebrate Shark Week more than once a year by storing your tampons and pads inside this Shark Week period pouch. Each brightly colored pouch sports a black “Shark Week” logo and comes with a zippered opening for bloody quick access.

Give your new tech some old school flair by protecting it using this retro Walkman iPhone case. This custom rubber case fits snuggly around your phone, provides quick access to all its buttons and features, and comes with a totally rad 1980s styled Walkman design.

titleEN: Star Wars AT-AT Family Car Stickers
content: Showcase every Imperial in your little army with these Star Wars AT-AT family car stickers. They’re handmade from white adhesive vinyl and come in sets featuring two AT-ATs to represent the parents and a pair of smaller AT-STs for the kids or pets.

Show your selfie queen you’re a match made in narcissistic heaven with this Kim and Kanye necklace set. Each plastic pendant features the beautiful mug of one half of the glorified power couple attached to a lovely silver chain.

Give the old tool belt a fun prehistoric touch by equipping yourself with these Jurassic multi-tools. It features a copper etched Jurassic crocodile that comes with built-in screwdrivers, box cutters, bottle openers, and hex wrenches.

Increase your chances of survival once all hell breaks loose by keeping your skills sharp using these zombie archery targets. Each target is handmade from archery foam and decorated like a revolting zombie torso that you get to impale over and over again.

Keep your literature organized while giving your room a modern feel using this industrial pipe shelf. Each shelf is handmade from beautifully aged Oak wood – available in four different finishes – and is complemented by sturdy galvanized steel pipes.

Prove you’re the ultimate Star Wars fan in the galaxy by acquiring these stunningly detailed patent posters. The set includes six posters depicting the blueprints for some of the most iconic vehicles like the X-Wing, AT-AT, and Millennium Falcon.

Set your manicure apart from all the others by using this visually compelling glitter nail polish. This unique polish is custom blended with a mixture of micas, glitter, and other colorants that combine to create a striking multicolored pattern.

Keep your stuff organized while complementing the rustic decor of your room using these gorgeous driftwood shelves. They’re handmade with utmost craftsmanship and are connected via a strong steel cable to provide added stability.

Feel a little more fabulous while you perform mundane chores around the house by wearing one of these Disney princess aprons. These handmade aprons come in a range of colorful styles that include Cinderella, Aurora, Ariel, Elsa, and Belle.

Accent your sleek phone’s modern design with a little natural beauty by protecting it with this dried pressed flowers smartphone case. It’s decorated with a lovely tree made out of pressed flowers and is designed to easily snap on.

Show off your love for our beloved planet by sporting this Earth watch. It features Japanese quartz movement, displays the North American continent in stunning color throughout its entire face, and can be customized with either faux or genuine leather bands.

Brace yourselves – poop is coming after you chug down a hearty cup of coffee using this Game Of Thrones themed mug. With a capacity of eleven ounces, the mug is dishwasher and microwave safe and can also be personalized to your liking.

Make your urban space feel a little more like nature by lighting up one of these outdoor scented candles. These soy wax candles are handmade from natural ingredients and feature delightful nature inspired scents like ‘bonfire’ and ‘cabin’.

Give your kitchen an international feel by bringing home a piece of jolly ol’ England with this UK telephone box fridge wrap. It’s handmade from vinyl and depicts both the outside and inside of the telephone booth to create an incredibly life-like effect.

Remove the grime without irritating your skin from harmful chemicals by cleaning yourself with this rough stuff natural soap bar. Ingredients like shea butter and coconut oil combine with coffee grounds and bamboo charcoal for a deep exfoliation and cleansing.

Give your works of art a little prehistoric flair by drawing them using these dinosaur shaped crayons. The set is handmade from non-toxic pigment and soy wax and come shaped like a variety of dinosaurs – such as the T-Rex, Triceratops, and the Stegosaurus.

Lug around all your gear without tying up your hands by placing it inside this black leather hip bag. It sports three different compartments to keep your things organized, and straps comfortably onto your waist and leg so you can easily access it.

Help your complexion stay youthful and healthy by exfoliating yourself with this zombie scrub dead skin remover. It’s made using natural ingredients like pure cane sugar, honey, sweet almond oil, and possesses a delightful eucalyptus scent.

Piece together the perfect Dorothy costume by topping off your ensemble with these lovely ruby slippers. These one of a kind pumps come fully decked out in red sequence along with red gems, rhinestones, and bugle beads.

Give any room in your home an antiquated feel by placing this vintage Kodak Eastman camera on display. Made in the early twentieth century, this gorgeous and antique Kodak Junior No. 3A folding camera makes the perfect gift for the photographer in your life.

Experience total bliss next time you’re craving something sweet by biting into one of these Oreo chocolate brownies. These delectable brownies are handmade using all natural ingredients and are complemented with huge chunks of Oreo cookies.

Diamonds are nice, but nothing says “I Love You” <del>and I’m broke</del> quite like this LEGO engagement ring. It sports a sizeable clear LEGO brick rock and can be customized with a plastic band available in a range of vibrant hues.

The stunning hue of this glowing blue rose necklace will ensure you get noticed wherever you go – day or night. The necklace features a lovely glass vial pendant that encases a small rose that comes alive under UV lighting.

Give your hair a striking appearance by coloring it using this non-permanent hair dye chalk. It’s made from non-toxic materials that won’t harm your hair, goes on easily without any fuss, and will last for up to two washes.

Give your reading nook an out of this galaxy touch by organizing your library using these Death Star bookends. They come designed like the iconic partially constructed weaponized space station and feature non-slip cork bottoms to keep them from sliding.

Keep your doobie in perfect condition until it’s time to blaze it up by storing it in this leather joint carrying case. It sports a tough solid brass interior and a stylish handcrafted leather exterior so your jay remains unbent and unbroken while you’re on the go.

Ensure the bride-to-be’s last night as a single woman ends with a bang by playing these bachelorette party games. This instant download comes with 3 fun games including bachelorette bingo, “drink if…”, and a scavenger hunt.

Help melt your stress away by soaking in a steamy tub filled with these eucalyptus bath bombs. Each bath bomb releases skin-soothing oils that contain a pleasant scent and won’t ever leave your skin feeling greasy or oily.

Turn heads at your next nighttime soiree by accenting your formal wear with one of these glowing pocket squares. They feature a built-in lithium battery that you can recharge via USB and are available in one of five classy hues.

Enjoy having your favorite food every night without gaining a single pound by accenting your outfit with these Chinese takeout container earrings. They feature hypoallergenic nickel hooks and are made to look like a yummy box of Chinese noodles.

Create unique aesthetically pleasing letters using this antique alphabet stamp set. Crafted from rubber and wood, this 70 piece set features the entire alphabet in both lower case and capital letters, and comes neatly arranged in a wooden case for easy transport.

Feel accomplished after a hard day in the real world by rewarding yourself with one of these hilarious adulting stickers. They come printed with messages like “I wore a bra today!” and “I put away the laundry!” so you can celebrate almost any half-assed effort!

Prepare for battle on the icy planet of Hoth by slipping into this Star Wars X-Wing pilot jumpsuit. This hand-tailored costume is made to your exact measurements to ensure a perfect fit and is styled exactly like the suit from the movie for ultimate authenticity.

Place your Jedi weaponry on display by showcasing it on this Star Wars themed stand. This 16 inch long structure is handcrafted using laser-cut stainless steel and outfitted with LEDs at the base which you can customize with one of eleven colors.

Add a little whimsy to your kid’s playroom using this scaredy mice mousehole wall sticker. This small handmade vinyl decal creates the illusion a group of mice are cowering in fear inside their cartoon-like mousehole in the wall.

It’s dangerous to leave the bathroom with unwashed hands – with delightful scents like rosemary citrus and black cherry, these Zelda rupee soap bars come in one of six vivid colors including orange, red, purple, green, yellow, and blue.

Easily play your favorite strategy game on the go by bringing along this 2D portable chess set. Each square on the board features a narrow slit that allows you to easily insert the flat pieces – creating a compact fold up package that you can take anywhere.

Give your lips an eye-catching shimmering effect using this pink glitter lip gloss. It’s made from natural ingredients like aloe vera extract and shea butter and is complemented by holographic glitter that sparkles and makes your lips pop.

Give your home a distinguished hunter’s lodge feel without having to shed any blood using these paper animal trophy head kits. This fun DIY project shows you how to create amazing and exotic animal busts using nothing more than paper and glue.

titleEN: Froot Loops Scented Cereal Bowl Candle
content: Enjoy a bowl of your favorite cereal without gaining an ounce of weight by lighting up this Froot Loops scented cereal bowl candle. Complemented with a real spoon, this 12 ounce candle comes with three wicks and looks so good you’ll be hard pressed not to have a spoonful!

Give any part of your home a delicious bakery aroma by lighting up this doughnut scented candle. This handmade soy wax candle comes in a quaint mason jar and features a delightful doughnut scent with hints of cinnamon and frosting.

Set your formal attire apart from the rest by accenting it using these skull cufflinks. Handcrafted from bone, rosewood, and aged brass, each Italian made cufflink features a cool skull and crossbones design that’ll make your formal wear truly pop.

Prove you’re the ultimate anime fan in your circle of friends by dressing up in this Ampharos inspired onesie. This handmade onesie features adorable accents like ears and a long tail and is crafted from anti-pill polar fleece that provides a warm and comfy fit.

Make your little crime fighter’s dreams come true by transforming him into a superhero with one of these personalized kid’s superhero capes. These small capes can be customized with a specific color scheme and superhero name.

Let that special someone know they’re the one you choose by giving them these pokeball duct tape roses. These handmade roses are crafted using different colored tape to recreate a blooming rose any Pokegeek will love.

Hold the door! Hold the door! Hold the door! Hold the door! Hold the door! Hold the door! Hold the door! Hold the door! Hold the dor! Hold the dor! Hold the dor! Hol de dor! Hol de dor! Hol de dor! Holdor! Holdor! Hodor! Hodor! Hodor… Hodor…

Upstage every monster and ghoul you encounter walking the streets this All Hallows Eve by dressing up in this realistic spider costume. The costume is skillfully handcrafted to resemble a giant 6 foot arachnid that’ll terrify anyone.

Play a mean yet funny joke on guests when they visit your home with these gummy bear shaped soaps. The pack includes 5 multi colored 2.5 ounce glycerin soap bars skillfully sculpted into cuddly little bears with a delightful fruity fragrance.

Enjoy afternoon tea with the Dark Lord  by drinking out of this Cthulhu tea cup. You must not question his strange ablutions – but rather treasure the time you spend with the great gelatinous cephalopod lord and the blessings he will bestow upon you.

Solidify the bond between you and your best bud like only two geeks can with this Batman and Robin friendship necklace. Each half comes decorated in the likeness of the dynamic duo’s classic superhero ensembles.

Marvel at the majesty of the universe every time you go spend some moola with this galaxy leather wallet. It sports a sleek and thin profile that won’t create a bulk in your pants and features five pockets for all your credit cards, ID, and cash.

Take your favorite caffeinated beverage on the go in true wizard fashion by placing it inside this “Espresso Patronum” travel mug. It’s made from durable plastic and is complemented by a clever pun and a golden glittery base.

Spice up your home’s bland decor with a little eastern flair with this hanging mandala tapestry. It’s handcrafted from cotton and displays an incredibly intricate circular design reminiscent of patterns used by cultures all around the world.

Bring your favorite Game Of Thrones character to life by dressing up this Jon Snow Night’s Watch cloak. It’s handmade using faux fur and accents like genuine leather straps and metallic buckles to pull off a realistic film quality look.

Take an anthophilian approach to adding storage space to your home by installing these wooden honeycomb shelves. The elegant geometric shape makes them ideal for either hanging on the wall or placing on a desktop.

Give your bedroom an otherworldly glow by lighting the place up using this Aliens queen lamp. It emits a cool red glow from the center and is skillfully handcrafted from recycled metals in the form of the sinister queen from the iconic sci-fi film series.

Turn playtime into snack time by digging into these solid chocolate LEGO bricks. Inspired by the iconic building toy, each piece of chocolate features a colorful brick-like exterior and is available in a variety of flavors like dark, milk, and white chocolate.

Fill your child with joy and wonder when she loses her teeth by leaving this tooth fairy copper pressed penny under her pillow. It’s perfect for perpetuating your deceitful lies about a visit from the tooth fairy – setting the groundwork for trust issues for years to come.

Give your wardrobe a cosmic touch that’ll draw attention wherever you go by dressing up in these galaxy Doc Martens. The boots come hand painted with a marvelously unique pattern of the cosmos painted over the entire surface.

Transform your little warrior into an imposing Norse raider by dressing him up in this baby viking hat and beard beanie. It’s hand knit from premium acrylic and designed to warm your little viking’s cranium with a mean looking horned helmet and thick beard.

Create eye-catching treats that any little girl would go crazy for with these Disney princess cake pop toppers. The PDF comes with 13 different princesses like Ariel, Mulan, and Jasmine – and can be used to top off treats like cake pops or cupcakes.

titleEN: Glow In The Dark Galaxy Hoodie
content: Become the center of attention when you hit the club dressed in this glow in the dark galaxy hoodie. This bodysuit hoodie is handmade from lycra spandex for a light and comfy fit and comes decorated with a brilliant image of the cosmos that reacts under UV light.

Upgrade your humble abode’s curb appeal by bringing in this recycled metal Transformer statue. This metallic work of art is composed entirely from recycled automobile and bike parts in the likeness of the iconic Bumblebee.

Turn your garden into the crown jewel of the block by sprinkling in some color with this magical unicorn poop. The small statue displays a flurry of color along its delightful surface and is complemented by gorgeous diamonds that truly make this poop pop.

Keep all eyes on you as you shred down the slopes wearing this panda balaclava. This one-size-fits-all accessory is skillfully handmade from a 100% cotton knit and is accented by two adorable black little panda ears.

Add a dash of whimsy to any plain bedroom with one of these papercraft unicorn heads. After downloading the PDF file, the template will guide you step by step so you can transform a flat sheet of paper into a majestic multicolored unicorn.

Take comfort and style to the next level when the weather drops by staying warm in this turtleneck jumpsuit. You’ll feel like you’re inside a warm fuzzy cloud once you slip into this one of a kind hand-knitted sheep’s wool garment.

Turn your pooch into the noblest warrior at the dog park by dressing him in this heavy suit of armor. It can be customized to accommodate different breeds and is designed to cover just the top of the torso, so your dog can move freely.

titleEN: You Are Just So, So Old Card
content: Get a rise out of your loved one before surprising him with a heartfelt message by giving him this “You Are Just So, So Old” card. The clever fold disguises the full length of the message with a humorous joke guaranteed to get some laughs.

Send your eyes end taste buds on an incredibly delicious journey by digging into this rainbow salted caramel cheesecake. This visually captivating treat is handmade to order using top shelf ingredients for the best possible taste.

Lift your spirits with butter beer’s intoxicating aroma even if you don’t have a mug of the stuff nearby using this soy scented candle. It’s made from eco-friendly soy wax and comes in a quaint little mason glass jar so you can place it virtually anywhere.

Set yourself apart from the pack by expressing your unique fashion sense with this snail shell helmet. This crazy looking accessory is made from a thin and lightweight urethane rubber designed to create the illusion your head is one giant hairy slug.

Comfort food takes on a whole new meaning with these hamburger scatter cushions in your living room. Each cushion in the set comes shaped like a different ingredient  of the hamburger – allowing for endless possibilities.

Prove you’re the ultimate GOT fan by decorating your entertainment room’s wall with this Game of Thrones periodic table. Each element square in the table reveals information and spoilers about every facet of the immensely popular series.

Blur the lines between the real and virtual world by transforming yourself into a pixelated character using this Minecraft costume kit. It comes fully painted with Velcro straps along the back so you can easily put it on.

Make Taco Tuesdays a little extra special by slipping into these outrageous pink taco panties. They’re made from pink lace and cotton knit for a comfortable fit and feature a couple of brightly colored pink hard shells tacos with all the fixings.

Make your favorite sitcom come alive like never before by unleashing your artistic talents on this Friends coloring book. The book comes filled with 12 pages of content featuring the show’s beloved characters in some of their most memorable scenes.

Turn exciting experiences into treasured memories that’ll last a lifetime by writing them down in this adventure travel journal. It comes with over 230 blank A5 sized pages and is complemented by a stunning full color vintage map over the cover.

Straight out of bat country comes this incredibly sculpted Fear And Loathing In Las Vegas pipe made in the image of Johnny Depp’s iconic character. It’s handmade from fine terracotta and features an ample sized bowl built into the top of the head.

Give your look a far-out cosmic appearance by applying some of this rainbow highlighter makeup. The makeup creates a bright and shiny metallic effect and is made from all natural vegan-friendly materials that won’t harm the skin.

Bone up on your basic chemistry while you sip out of this water molecules drinking glass. The long cylindrical shape holds up to 15 ounces and comes printed with small H20 molecules floating all along the surface – making this a great gift for chemistry geeks.

Next to the loofah and special salts, the wooden bathtub caddy is the one thing you don’t want to bathe without. It provides a convenient and dry place for your books, candles, and even your electronic devices – if you’re feeling bold.

Add a geeky touch to any part of your home by anthropomorphizing your wall outlets using this cool Batman decal. This fun little decal is handmade in the image of the Caped Crusader and can be removed and reapplied without losing its stickiness.

Sweeten up your look by showing your favorite breakfast food some love with these cereal nail decals. Each water-activated decal displays detailed images of your favorite cereals like Frosted Flakes and Lucky Charms in brilliant color and detail.

These handmade bath bombs are the ultimate cure for a hectic day. They’re available in a range of exotic scents and custom made using the finest ingredients designed to nourish your skin and leave it feeling smooth and moisturized.

Make your fruit salads looks even more delicious than they already are by serving them in these vibrant watermelon bowls. The set comes with one large serving bowl and four smaller ones – all hand painted in a fun watermelon design.

titleEN: LEGO Breaking Bad Meth Lab Playset
content: Get the upright citizens of LEGOville hooked on the blue stuff using this LEGO Breaking Bad meth lab playset. LEGO Walter White and Jesse Pinkman come dressed in their iconic orange jumpsuits ready to cook the finest crystal this side of the border.

Bring some rustic charm into your drab workspace by saving your documents on this solid oak USB flash drive. It’s handcrafted from gorgeous solid oak and optionally comes encased in an equally eye-catching custom wooden box case.

titleEN: This Is Why I Squat Tank Top
content: Show off your sculpted assets in a cheeky manner with this “This Is Why I Squat” tank top. It’s available in a range of vibrant hues and comes adorned with a design that averts all attention to your perfectly formed derrière.

Achieve your lifelong dream of becoming a Pokemon master by acquiring these Kanto League Pokemon badges. Each badge is handcrafted from polystyrene and fitted with tie-tack pins on the back so you can easily place them on any garment.

Send your little muggles on the emotional roller coaster of their young lives by presenting them with this Hogwarts acceptance letter. The package includes everything from a Hogwarts express ticket to a late delivery apology from Dumbledore himself.

Become the center of attention during your next skate session by accessorizing with these roller skate lights. The lights measure 9.8 inches long and come with an adhesive backing so you can easily place them on your skates.

Ensure your fresh baked bread remains warm and makes it home in one piece by toting it in this baguette bag. Made from 100% cotton, the bag measures 21.6 inches long and comes with an adjustable strap for easy carrying.

titleEN: Not A Stripper Mother’s Day Card
content: Let mom know she did a great job of raising you by presenting her with this “Congrats – I’m Not A Stripper” card. You may have not become a doctor or lawyer like she wanted, but at least she can rest easy knowing you’re not shaking it out there for loose change.
